lyrics:
(Verse 1)
Listen up, I'm here to drop a rhyme,
Spittin' fire, it's my time to shine.
From the streets to the stage, I'm in my zone,
With every beat, I'm setting the tone.

(Verse 2)
Got dreams so big, they reach the sky,
Gonna hustle hard, never asking why.
From the struggles I face, I'll rise above,
In this game of life, I'm gonna show some love.

(Chorus)
Rap is my language, beats my fuel,
In this world of rhythm, I make my rule.
With every verse, I'm breaking free,
Living life to the fullest, just being me.
